Class UserEndpoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.softserve.taf.services.common.AbstractWebEndpoint
      • UserEndpoint
  • public class UserEndpoint
extends com.softserve.taf.services.common.AbstractWebEndpoint
    This class is an implementation of AbstractWebEndpoint and it provides operations for creating, updating, retrieving individual and all users from the server.
